            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Call Recorder 0.1.0</h2>
                <p>Initial release with full call recording functionality:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Two-track recording (microphone + system audio)</li>
                    <li>Automatic call detection</li>
